===Latin===

===Noun Phrase===
'''lapis philosophi'''

# philosopher's stone, a mythical device to use in magic

====Usage Note====
Used in the title and plot of the first [[Harry Potter]] novel by 
Rowling.  In the U.S. the title was changed to ''Harry Potter and the Sorcerer's Stone''.

